A Mdantsane woman found a badly decomposed body in front of her house this morning. Tulisa Mqingwana of NU5 said she noticed something covered in a window curtains when she returned from work last night.&#8220;I didn&#8217;t pay much attention to it,&#8221; she said.She said it was this morning when she took a closer look and realised that the &#8220;rubbish&#8221; that she saw outside her house was in fact remains of a decomposed body.Police and forensic team were at the scene this morning.